snippet.title: Conqueror's Blade: Season II - Wrath of the Nomads Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Smash new challenges, unlock exclusive rewards, and discover the mighty Sons of the Steppes unit line in Conqueror’s Blade Season II: Wrath of the Nomads, available to download for free today!
